==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
From the alternate of [[πίπτω]] {{GG|4098}}; 

===Pronunciation===
*πτῶμα / ptōma / pto'-mah

===Noun===
'''πτῶμα'''

# a [[ruin]], that is, (specifically) lifeless body ([[corpse]], [[carrion]]): - dead [[body]], carcase, corpse.

